      "content": "Here is a draft focusing on traditional values. \"Friends, neighbors, fellow patriots, we stand at a crossroads where the foundational values of our nation are under relentless assault. They seek to rewrite the very meaning of family, to dismantle the bedrock institutions that have made this country great. We must stand unapologetically for the traditional family—the bedrock of American life—and defend our children from the corrosive tide of radical ideologies. Let's send a clear message: our values are not for sale!\"",
